{"tid":2292894,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"鄧 炳 強 上 任 一 年 黑 暴 罪 惡 跌 ５ 成","createTime":"2020-11-20T00:34:49.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-20T09:34:53.000Z","uid":82845,"like":19,"dislike":497,"uniUserReply":124,"replies":[{"pid":"d2d8dfd2bf7eeff1df47b3baf7d3128364354521","tid":2292894,"uid":82845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-20T00:34:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EV8YxdK.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEV8YxdK.jpg&h=b8fbadcc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"x-large\">鄧直言，上任一年來面對的兩大困難是警隊被抹黑及警員被起底，並說：「警隊於過去175年聲譽良好，<span class=\"red\">但去年卻被大肆抹黑，如8．31死人，新屋嶺拘留中心及警署發生性侵事件，這些虛假的消息對警隊有極大影響</span>，幸隨着法庭審訊，將事件暴露出來，陸續呈現是虛假指控。」而警方亦會盡快澄清這些假消息，包括進行現場直播，將真相向市民呈現。</span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20201119/bkn-20201119033020869-1119_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20201119%2Fbkn-20201119033020869-1119_00822_001.html&d=kK8wO%2BHHGyY98lbbYtfopWCvuqnjOb%2FiGpmC2gL%2Fng4%3D&h=bf632d89\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20201119/bkn-20201119033020869-1119_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"5be888e558b10ab81a57e0bba504afc6e6077808","tid":2292894,"uid":39710,"like":142,"dislike":4,"score":138,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-20T00:35:24.000Z","msg":"白粉收皮啦"},{"pid":"e58cc1557d312e6842f4de71620d9284ee0b8441","tid":2292894,"uid":96871,"like":313,"dislike":2,"score":311,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-20T00:35:54.000Z","msg":"上任一年 香港個地位跌到仆街唔提<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c752a0c2a890acc73b595f44e228971ec76c753","tid":2292894,"uid":151074,"like":310,"dislike":1,"score":309,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2020-11-20T00:36:37.000Z","msg":"炳強上任一年已還清中銀按揭<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/